4
[div class=p 
	[a class=intlink href=/Users/Profile/FractalFusion 
		"FractalFusion
	]a
	"'s Mega Man X in 29:58. It is 2762 frames (~46 seconds) faster than the published run. I decided this game should get an improved run, so I started working on it after my 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=Monopoly run|href=/717M)
	". Keep in mind that I was busy over the 2.5 months I worked on this run, and I had previously been working on a Mega Man X2 improvement (even before I knew about 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=parrot14gree's MMX2 run|href=/698M)
	" as well as Splinter Cell for GBA.
	$LF
]div
