		" Intro skip
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Dashing and shooting an uncharged X-Buster, which does 2 damage instead of 1 to enemies (except Sigma and Final Sigma).
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Shooting while charged and remaining charged.
		$LF
